# Exception: commit the native-runtime export venv's lockfile (the whole point
# of the uv-native conversion in 230d370 is reproducible installs from a
# committed lockfile; without uv.lock, `uv sync` re-resolves on every install
# and reproducibility drifts as upstream packages release).
